0:02:32.100,0:02:33.090
Why don't you come inside?

0:02:33.560,0:02:35.080
Do you think I'm going to eat you?

0:02:36.310,0:02:36.970
I dare not.

0:02:38.440,0:02:42.480
You look as if we have become enemies.

0:02:43.940,0:02:47.400
May I ask what Your Highness calls me for?

0:02:48.030,0:02:49.400
There's a suspicion in my mind.

0:02:50.120,0:02:52.860
I hope taking my pulse will bring some clarity.

0:02:54.250,0:02:54.830
Yes.

0:03:18.190,0:03:18.840
My Lady ...

0:03:19.810,0:03:21.034
It seems

0:03:21.449,0:03:24.171
my dream came true.

0:03:25.940,0:03:26.680
Is it...

0:03:28.000,0:03:29.240
is it from that night?

0:03:38.407,0:03:41.410
Don't bother telling me this is a crime
 that will get my whole clan executed.

0:03:42.750,0:03:44.160
This is my child.

0:03:45.710,0:03:49.600
I'll protect him with my life; 
I'll ensure he has a peaceful life.

0:03:51.220,0:03:54.180
Shichu, please help me.

0:03:55.010,0:03:58.880
Do not let this dream turn into a nightmare.

0:04:04.900,0:04:06.951
Is this the time when His Majesty comes back from the court?

0:04:07.740,0:04:08.980
Yes, I have confirmed it.

0:04:09.740,0:04:13.720
Then look hard for it.

0:04:26.630,0:04:29.750
What are you looking for here so early?

0:04:30.510,0:04:32.090
Peace to Your Majesty.

0:04:35.600,0:04:36.960
I lost a bracelet.

0:04:37.470,0:04:38.510
I wouldn't care so much, but

0:04:39.100,0:04:41.930
Your Majesty granted it to me my first year in the palace.

0:04:42.560,0:04:44.020
I cherish it dearly.

0:04:44.560,0:04:45.360
Su Peisheng.

0:04:45.520,0:04:46.100
Your Majesty.

0:04:46.400,0:04:47.120
Help find the bracelet.

0:04:47.190,0:04:47.810
Aye.

0:04:55.780,0:04:58.900
You don't dress in bright colors often.

0:05:00.450,0:05:03.490
You look graceful and endearing in this dress.

0:05:04.290,0:05:07.600
The dress is honored to gain Your Majesty's compliment.

0:05:11.130,0:05:12.512
Your Majesty, we found the bracelet.

0:05:19.810,0:05:21.300
Don't be concerned if you lose it again.

0:05:21.810,0:05:22.995
There are plenty in the storehouse.

0:05:23.720,0:05:26.152
No replacement would have the affection I hold for this one.

0:05:26.520,0:05:29.230
Your Majesty's favorite tea has been prepared at the Palace of Pearl Jade.

0:05:29.480,0:05:30.860
Will Your Majesty come?

0:05:31.780,0:05:33.770
How can I decline since you have prepared it?

0:05:39.483,0:05:42.160
Did the sun ... come out from the west today?

0:05:42.910,0:05:44.820
"Little rabbits," follow!

0:05:52.800,0:05:53.630
You're here.

0:05:54.510,0:05:55.340
Find a chair.

0:05:56.180,0:05:58.210
Lunar, go cut some fruit.

0:05:58.430,0:05:59.090
Yes.

0:06:00.680,0:06:02.970
You've been living with great modesty these years.

0:06:03.730,0:06:05.760
This dress was made the year I left.

0:06:07.190,0:06:10.560
I picked out some fine fabrics for you,
 to make new dresses.

0:06:11.230,0:06:12.520
You are sending me everything.

0:06:12.960,0:06:14.400
You've only been back for a few months,

0:06:14.490,0:06:17.120
but my palace is going to overflow from your gifts.

0:06:17.120,0:06:18.560
Yes, but now you are all stocked up.

0:06:25.750,0:06:27.160
Your Highness Consort Lumière is also here.

0:06:28.130,0:06:31.210
Peace to Consort Lumière.
Peace to Concubine Vertu.

0:06:32.670,0:06:33.380
Your Highness,

0:06:34.050,0:06:36.040
these are gifts from His Majesty.

0:06:36.340,0:06:37.130
Please accept them.

0:06:37.760,0:06:38.800
Lunar, take them.

0:06:41.850,0:06:43.630
Mr. Su, thank you for coming here.

0:06:44.980,0:06:48.260
Please take these to buy some tea.

0:06:48.690,0:06:49.680
I'm unworthy.

0:06:53.360,0:06:54.350
These are too valuable.

0:06:55.690,0:06:56.635
I thank Your Highness.

0:06:57.740,0:07:00.880
His Majesty said these gifts are meant to ease your boredom, Your Highness.

0:07:01.370,0:07:02.980
Please also get prepared, Your Highness.

0:07:03.450,0:07:06.760
The Phoenix Carriage will be here to pick you up tonight.

0:07:08.000,0:07:10.540
Please thank His Majesty for me.

0:07:11.880,0:07:13.240
Allow me to take my leave.

0:07:18.720,0:07:19.580
Congratulations.

0:07:20.760,0:07:22.130
Is it your luck changing,

0:07:22.720,0:07:24.090
or is it your temper?

0:07:25.350,0:07:28.090
It's neither good nor bad,

0:07:28.730,0:07:30.180
nor related to luck or temper.

0:07:31.480,0:07:32.940
One has to keep living.

0:07:33.400,0:07:36.360
Life ... has to move forward.

0:07:44.620,0:07:45.150
Su Peisheng.

0:07:45.410,0:07:46.120
Yes.

0:07:46.450,0:07:48.990
Consort Lumière is pregnant. Serve her the plum soup.

0:07:49.210,0:07:51.700
Your Majesty, I had the plum soup ready in advance.

0:07:57.760,0:07:58.420
Your Majesty,

0:07:58.760,0:08:01.040
the plum soup looks appetizing.

0:08:01.510,0:08:03.630
Please ask Consort Lumière for a serving for me.

0:08:04.050,0:08:05.210
I know you can drink.

0:08:06.100,0:08:08.970
Su Peisheng, fill up Concubine Vertu's wine cup.

0:08:09.310,0:08:09.920
Aye.

0:08:14.230,0:08:15.020
Your Majesty,

0:08:16.070,0:08:17.600
I'm pregnant,

0:08:17.940,0:08:19.060
so I should avoid drinking.

0:08:21.410,0:08:22.520
Since when?

0:08:23.570,0:08:24.600
How many months has it been?

0:08:24.780,0:08:26.570
I felt unwell yesterday,

0:08:27.040,0:08:28.370
so I called in Dr. Wen.

0:08:29.120,0:08:30.530
He told me I've been pregnant for two months.

0:08:31.750,0:08:32.530
Very well.

0:08:33.580,0:08:35.950
Indeed it should be two months.

0:08:38.050,0:08:38.910
Congratulations, Concubine Vertu.

0:08:43.140,0:08:44.360
Since Concubine Vertu is pregnant,

0:08:45.010,0:08:45.970
- Su Peisheng.
- Yes.

0:08:46.140,0:08:49.840
Change Concubine Vertu's dishes to be the same as Consort Lumière's.

0:08:50.060,0:08:50.720
Yes.

0:08:51.730,0:08:52.590
This summer,

0:08:53.270,0:08:55.390
the chrysanthemums in the harem bloomed much earlier.

0:08:56.770,0:08:58.980
I was worried that it was an ill omen.

0:08:59.990,0:09:02.850
Now it seems it was auspicious.

0:09:04.490,0:09:06.860
Huan Huan and Meizhuang are both pregnant.

0:09:08.370,0:09:11.530
There has never been such a joyful time in the harem.

0:09:15.880,0:09:17.740
Now you have become the most precious.

0:09:18.670,0:09:20.831
The Empress Dowager sends health tonics every day.

0:09:21.380,0:09:23.840
And the Empress sends Autumn over three times a day.

0:09:24.720,0:09:26.130
It's annoying to see Autumn here.

0:09:26.640,0:09:29.360
I have to fake a smile despite knowing she's up to no good.

0:09:29.810,0:09:30.920
It's exhausting.

0:09:31.560,0:09:32.300
Indeed.

0:09:33.140,0:09:34.550
The Empress has been sick for months.

0:09:35.060,0:09:37.320
Meanwhile, two high-ranking concubines got pregnant.

0:09:37.820,0:09:38.980
Of course she is anxious.

0:09:40.150,0:09:42.310
This time, even if she has "three heads and six arms,"

0:09:42.310,0:09:43.980
she can't handle it all.

0:09:46.070,0:09:48.440
Just save yourself from any mental labor.

0:09:49.700,0:09:52.280
Remember to have a light diet.

0:09:52.620,0:09:55.110
Don't drink too much tea or eat too much spicy food.

0:09:55.710,0:09:57.660
Keep away from any incense.

0:09:58.840,0:10:02.920
Your belly becomes bigger and 
your words become more maternal.

0:10:03.420,0:10:07.816
I've been getting an earful of these words,
and my ears are almost growing calluses.

0:10:08.850,0:10:10.200
My good intention is wasted, it seems.

0:10:11.600,0:10:14.440
I'm glad the Empress Dowager sent 
Wen Shichu to take care of your pregnancy.

0:10:15.140,0:10:17.350
I don't trust anyone else.

0:10:17.980,0:10:19.440
If Her Majesty sent someone else,

0:10:20.020,0:10:21.100
I wouldn't accept them.

0:10:22.110,0:10:25.160
He has been taking care of my health all these years.

0:10:25.780,0:10:29.880
I won't believe a word from any other imperial doctors.

0:10:30.450,0:10:33.070
You have been pregnant for almost eight months.

0:10:33.870,0:10:39.130
I'm pregnant for less than three months.
It's the most unstable time for pregnancy.

0:10:39.130,0:10:40.790
He must be exhausted looking after us both.

0:10:41.590,0:10:42.920
This is hard work for him.

0:10:43.260,0:10:45.000
As long as you and your child are safe and healthy,

0:10:45.220,0:10:48.240
his effort over these years will be recognized.

0:10:48.680,0:10:49.380
Right.

0:10:50.330,0:10:53.096
This child came unexpectedly,

0:10:54.430,0:10:58.480
but I will do everything to protect it.

0:11:00.000,0:11:01.965
Even though you don't forgive His Majesty,

0:11:02.940,0:11:04.900
the child is innocent, after all.

0:11:04.900,0:11:07.440
The emperor is the emperor, and my child is my child.

0:11:08.030,0:11:10.270
They cannot be mentioned on equal terms.

0:11:11.653,0:11:14.370
Meizhuang, don't lie in bed all day.

0:11:15.540,0:11:18.400
Let's go visit Consort Honnête with Consort Estime.

0:11:19.960,0:11:20.620
Sure.

0:11:22.210,0:11:25.920
Concubine Vertu got pregnant after many years in the harem.

0:11:26.260,0:11:32.000
Your good fortune makes me feel that
 even I have a life to look forward to.

0:11:37.020,0:11:39.130
I deserve punishment for being careless.

0:11:39.730,0:11:41.010
Peace to Your Highnesses.

0:11:45.110,0:11:46.140
Is His Majesty inside?

0:11:46.780,0:11:47.440
Yes.

0:11:47.690,0:11:49.810
His Majesty is visiting Consort Honnête.

0:11:50.860,0:11:53.280
How coincidental. We'll take our leave then.

0:11:53.780,0:11:54.680
Mr. Su,

0:11:55.240,0:11:58.400
having served His Majesty for so many years,
you deserve some rest now and then.

0:11:59.120,0:12:01.460
Otherwise, how would you have energy for all your tasks?

0:12:02.500,0:12:04.120
I thank Your Highness.

0:12:05.170,0:12:07.410
Sir, you dropped something.

0:12:10.040,0:12:10.800
Oh my.

0:12:12.390,0:12:13.040
Look at this.

0:12:14.140,0:12:16.250
How beautifully done!

0:12:16.810,0:12:19.720
It reminds me of Concubine Aide,
 who was best at weaving tassel knots.

0:12:20.270,0:12:22.720
But her knots aren't as fine as this one.

0:12:24.650,0:12:26.140
It seems to resemble your work.

0:12:27.860,0:12:29.730
Your Highness speaks too highly of me. I...

0:12:32.490,0:12:33.553
Take good care of it.

0:12:34.700,0:12:35.530
Thank you, Your Highness.

0:12:39.660,0:12:41.200
My Lady, Concubine An is here.

0:12:41.750,0:12:44.030
I hope my late-night visit doesn't disturb you, Meizhuang.

0:12:44.710,0:12:46.080
What brings you here, Lingrong?

0:12:46.840,0:12:49.170
I came specifically to congratulate you on your pregnancy.

0:12:49.630,0:12:51.420
I hope you don't mind that I invited myself.

0:12:51.800,0:12:53.920
Not at all. You've come at a good time.

0:12:54.340,0:12:56.798
I want to make a tiger-head hat for my child

0:12:57.288,0:13:00.000
to keep him warm as soon as he is born.

0:13:00.480,0:13:03.310
But I can't embroider the whiskers right.

0:13:04.060,0:13:04.963
Let me see.

0:13:26.040,0:13:26.950
How about this?

0:13:28.800,0:13:31.840
It looks very different now with your skilled hands.

0:13:33.050,0:13:37.560
It will look nicer if you add pearls onto the whiskers.

0:13:38.140,0:13:40.800
I like that idea. Teach me more, please.

0:13:47.940,0:13:49.400
My Lady, please have the prenatal tonic.

0:13:50.110,0:13:52.720
It's bad for your eyes to do needlework
 for too long during pregnancy.

0:13:53.070,0:13:53.860
Thank you very much, Dr. Wen.

0:13:59.740,0:14:01.200
I thank Your Majesty.

0:14:01.660,0:14:03.700
Your appetite is even worse than Consort Lumière's.

0:14:04.000,0:14:05.571
Are you not eating well these days?

0:14:06.000,0:14:07.200
You look unwell today.

0:14:08.090,0:14:11.560
My lady started to feel sick late last night,
and couldn't sleep well.

0:14:12.880,0:14:15.790
What was wrong? Have you called for a doctor?

0:14:16.090,0:14:17.050
The doctor said I'm fine.

0:14:17.550,0:14:18.960
But you look really unwell.

0:14:19.600,0:14:23.000
It might be because I got tired from
 talking to Lingrong last night.

0:14:23.430,0:14:24.800
I couldn't fall asleep after that.

0:14:25.060,0:14:26.000
Concubine An was here?

0:14:26.900,0:14:28.291
I thought she was in isolation.

0:14:28.770,0:14:31.920
Lingrong rarely comes, so I didn't want to turn her away.

0:14:32.400,0:14:34.060
After all, we are like sisters.

0:14:34.570,0:14:38.920
But My Lady ... You get unwell every time you see Concubine An.

0:14:40.030,0:14:40.841
Is that true?

0:14:41.870,0:14:43.080
I dare not lie to Your Majesty.

0:14:44.540,0:14:45.700
I know.

0:14:50.340,0:14:50.879
Tell Su Peisheng

0:14:51.991,0:14:52.960
to inform Concubine An

0:14:53.584,0:14:55.498
to stop coming to the Palace of Pearl Jade.

0:14:55.676,0:14:57.550
I don't want her to bring bad luck to Concubine Vertu.

0:14:57.752,0:14:58.332
Yes.

0:14:59.090,0:15:00.000
Have some porridge.

0:15:00.640,0:15:02.420
Yes. I thank Your Majesty.

0:15:02.934,0:15:04.880
How do you read this character?

0:15:05.270,0:15:06.080
Da. 
[大 large]

0:15:06.690,0:15:07.890
Longyue is so smart.

0:15:08.480,0:15:11.310
How about adding a dot under "da"?

0:15:12.110,0:15:13.080
Tai. 
[太 overly]

0:15:14.740,0:15:16.320
Very good, my Longyue.

0:15:17.150,0:15:18.640
Your Highness, the Fourth Prince is here.

0:15:19.110,0:15:19.920
Show him in.

0:15:23.990,0:15:25.239
Peace to Your Highness Consort Estime.

0:15:25.520,0:15:26.600
Gege. 
[elder brother]

0:15:26.910,0:15:29.400
What brings you here so early, Hongli?

0:15:29.710,0:15:31.760
I was passing by on my way to pay respects to Mother.

0:15:32.340,0:15:34.280
I hoped to pick up Longyue so she can come with me.

0:15:35.260,0:15:36.500
Fourth Prince, you are very well-mannered.

0:15:36.760,0:15:39.224
You come here to bring the Princess to the
Palace of Eternal Longevity every other day.

0:15:39.800,0:15:41.220
Longyue is the daughter of Mother.

0:15:41.220,0:15:43.840
It's only right for us to fulfill our filial duties to Mother.

0:15:45.140,0:15:47.350
Exactly. Go now so you can return early.

0:15:52.060,0:15:54.880
May I bring Longyue back after having breakfast
in the Palace of Eternal Longevity?

0:15:56.990,0:15:57.760
Certainly.

0:15:58.990,0:16:00.230
You two go with the princess.

0:16:00.700,0:16:01.400
Yes.

0:16:01.740,0:16:02.894
I'll take my leave, Your Highness.

0:16:20.220,0:16:21.050
Ruyi,

0:16:23.300,0:16:25.360
do you think Consort Lumière

0:16:26.039,0:16:28.140
told the Fourth Prince to do this?

0:16:29.000,0:16:30.010
Is she ...

0:16:32.980,0:16:35.270
really going to take Longyue away from me?

0:16:35.980,0:16:37.158
Don't overthink, Your Highness.

0:16:57.750,0:16:59.920
Your Majesty, Consort Estime came with me.

0:17:00.840,0:17:01.600
Bring her in.

0:17:02.510,0:17:03.120
Yes.

0:17:05.260,0:17:06.670
How is the Empress's illness?

0:17:07.470,0:17:09.400
Her Majesty has had a severe migraine for several days.

0:17:09.640,0:17:10.668
She's about to recover.

0:17:11.940,0:17:13.619
I'm afraid that after she recovers,

0:17:13.619,0:17:16.600
I'll have endless headaches.

0:17:20.030,0:17:22.360
Everyone thinks I've been pregnant for only eight months.

0:17:23.360,0:17:26.800
We need to have preparations for every circumstance.

0:17:28.030,0:17:28.971
Don't worry, Your Highness.

0:17:29.580,0:17:30.860
Everything is ready.

0:17:33.500,0:17:35.960
My due date is near.

0:17:37.000,0:17:40.120
But Concubine Vertu's pregnancy is in the 
first three months and not yet stable.

0:17:40.340,0:17:43.800
I entrust you with the safety of Concubine Vertu and her child.

0:17:46.702,0:17:47.670
What's wrong?

0:17:48.850,0:17:51.180
You look haggard these days.

0:17:52.980,0:17:55.340
My mind was wandering.

0:17:55.600,0:17:56.260
Nothing serious.

0:17:58.320,0:18:01.840
Now you are responsible for looking after
Concubine Vertu and me, and our children.

0:18:02.280,0:18:03.223
You must be exhausted.

0:18:04.320,0:18:07.720
But how can you take care of us
 if you don't look after yourself?

0:18:09.410,0:18:13.360
I used to think that as a doctor, 
I could cure people and save lives.

0:18:15.830,0:18:16.597
But ...

0:18:17.440,0:18:19.633
that's not the fact.

0:18:20.250,0:18:23.240
What makes you speak such discouraged words?

0:18:23.970,0:18:25.050
I'm not feeling discouraged.

0:18:25.880,0:18:27.970
But the longer I stay in the palace,

0:18:28.430,0:18:30.760
the more things are out of my control.

0:18:31.470,0:18:32.880
Everyone feels constrained.

0:18:33.180,0:18:34.510
Everyone has their difficulties.

0:18:35.390,0:18:36.630
Whatever happens, happens.

0:18:37.270,0:18:38.680
Just move forward, step by step.

0:18:39.400,0:18:40.713
But there are some things -

0:18:41.360,0:18:43.612
that I never thought would happen to me.

0:18:43.892,0:18:44.722
Does that matter?

0:18:45.700,0:18:47.480
A man has to face up to his own responsibilities.

0:18:48.740,0:18:51.320
No matter what you encounter, don't bow down to it.

0:18:52.240,0:18:53.381
Not only for yourself,

0:18:54.080,0:18:54.990
but also for others.

0:18:58.380,0:18:59.588
A man's responsibilities...

0:19:01.710,0:19:02.714
Your Highness.

0:19:03.590,0:19:04.750
No, Huan'er.

0:19:05.720,0:19:07.580
If I had made the biggest mistake...

0:19:08.340,0:19:10.430
would you forgive me?

0:19:12.359,0:19:13.756
Any mistakes you might have made -

0:19:13.756,0:19:15.226
I am not the one to forgive them.

0:19:15.730,0:19:17.340
As long as your heart has no regrets.

0:19:18.810,0:19:21.650
Otherwise, try your best to make up for it.

0:19:22.320,0:19:23.588
And don't repeat the same mistake.

0:19:25.990,0:19:27.213
You are exactly right, Huan'er.

0:19:29.030,0:19:30.900
I will do my best to

0:19:31.410,0:19:32.570
take care of Concubine Vertu.

0:19:33.030,0:19:34.950
Even if I have to "walk through fire and boiling water."

0:19:36.250,0:19:37.480
Allow me to take my leave.

